{"tid":1827710,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該(鍵戰)返返去抗爭101先啦->遊行集會。1.19 遮打道見","createTime":"2020-01-17T07:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T02:46:23.000Z","uid":175623,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6c9c3c9305b8ac1dd58d082739699a92239244d6","tid":1827710,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T07:08:39.000Z","msg":"【全球8國15市聯手，1.19 天下制裁大遊行！】<br />\n<br />\n攬炒團隊 同各國組織將會喺1.19同步發起遊行集會，支援 「民間集會團隊」發起嘅 1.19 港島東行《天下制裁大遊行》！<br />\n<br />\n即使面對嚴寒飛雪、史無前例山火，英美澳加紐德比等國居民 經過一個月籌備，仍然繼續聯手捍衛香港。<br />\n<br />\n謹此 懇切呼籲各地港人陸續響應號召，舉辦、參加1.19天下制裁行動，逆流打返起個勢！<br />\n<br />\n已確認1.19名單：<br />\n1. 香港 - 香港島<br />\n2. 美國 - 波士頓、洛杉磯、華盛頓特區、三藩市<br />\n3. 德國 - 柏林<br />\n4. 英國 - 倫敦、格拉斯哥<br />\n5. 澳洲 - 布里斯本 、墨爾本、悉尼<br />\n6. 紐西蘭 - 奧克蘭、基督城<br />\n7. 比利時 - 布魯塞爾<br />\n8. 加拿大 - 溫哥華<br />\n<br />\n至於各地詳情，請留意 &ldquo;Fight for Freedom. Stand with Hong Kong.&rdquo; Facebook page持續更新。<br />\n<br />\n上訴緊個no，但大家當日可以自決去港島行街食飯"},{"pid":"74bf8eda233a9fd1397304084aa98b3b644ae5e6","tid":1827710,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T07:09:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"944f7c2e41d1ebb7c3aead1518ad19819e0cb942","tid":1827710,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T07:12:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e4c1a16b47146e10621221418681174d82e6113","tid":1827710,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T07:16:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9bc60ea13c02740819bc8296c4a28b93e3a7c6","tid":1827710,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T07:16:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"345e4dfafc8a2b64f98368357ea764c2db11d996","tid":1827710,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T07:21:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ee821493ce7c7e81f3da09a063d68de851fb479","tid":1827710,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT